    "title": "Department Manager Vacancy at ProSport - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Department Manager with drive and ambition, ProSport in Gwalior is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout ProSport:\nProSport is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ProSport!",
